ents a shape consisting of one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"disconnected vertices, specified as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"text":" instances. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"points in the collection may be related but are not connected spatially. For","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"example, you could use a point collection to represent all the trees in an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"orchard.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection","title":"MLNPointCollection","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolyline":{"title":"MLNMultiPolyline","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"polylines. For example, you could use a multipolyline shape to represent both","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sides of a divided highway (dual carriageway), excluding the median (central","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reservation): each carriageway would be a distinct ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"},{"text":" object.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolyline","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolyline"}}}